body_html:
Is python 3.5 supported? Having the same problem in python 3.5.1

$ pip3 install --upgrade https://storage.googleapis.com/tensorflow/linux/cpu/tensorflow-0.6.0-cp34-none-linux_x86_64.whl
tensorflow-0.6.0-cp34-none-linux_x86_64.whl is not a supported wheel on this platform.

$ python --version
Python 3.5.1

$ uname -a
... 3.19.0-43-generic ... x86_64 GNU/Linux
